20¤Use, storage and disclosure of information
:SKRSLUT.
.of
.sp 3mm
.hy on
:SWISS8.
When you use your Dankort card, a record is made of information including
the card number, the transaction sum, the date of use and the location
where your Dankort card was used. This information is forwarded to
&BANKNAVN. by the business in question.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information is stored by the business, by the business's bank/Nets
and at &BANKNAVN..  &BANKNAVN. uses this information for bookkeeping,
in account statements and for subsequently correcting any errors.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information is only otherwise disclosed in cases where this is
required by law or to prevent misuse of the card. The information is
saved for the current year plus five years.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
