Digital wallet:
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A "Digital Wallet" is a personal software-based solution, where you
register your card data for future use in connection with Internet
purchases in a webshop.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Loyalty programmes
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Loyalty programmes is a general term for solutions, where cardholder can
register his/her card number with a benefit scheme provider and afterwards
earn personal bonus etc. or enrol a donation program.
