:FED.
Non-contact payment
:SKRSLUT.
.br
By means of the integrated sender, you can complete your payments at
businesses without inserting the card in the card terminal. You just have
to hold the card in a distance of 0-3 cm from the non-contact symbol on the
terminal when paying.
